  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    National Apprenticeship Awards 2020 national winners unveiled
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The best of England’s apprentice employers, apprentices, rising stars and individuals who champion apprenticeships have been announced during the 17th annual National Apprenticeship Awards.</p>

  </div>
</div>

